      • render

        public void render(boolean alone,
          boolean pathOnly,
          int w,
          int h,
          double minLat,
          double maxLat,
          double minLon,
          double maxLon,
          boolean showArrows,
          double zoom,
          java.awt.Graphics2D g2d)
        Render Path in Graphical representation.
        Parameters:
        alone - true if path is render alone (no more paths)
        pathOnly - true if paths are only objects rendering
        w - width of Canvas
        h - height of Canvas
        minLat - minimum Latitude coordinates of full system
        maxLat - maximum Latitude coordinates of full system
        minLon - minimum Longitude coordinates of full system
        maxLon - maximum Longitude coordinates of full system
        showArrows - true if showing road directions
        zoom - scale factor (modified when user zooms in/out)
        g2d - Graphics2D instance of Canvas
